w impacts your Google PageRank. I can make most pages load in under 1 second.'),(158,35,'_services_1_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(159,35,'services_2_icon','fa-lock fa-3x'),(160,35,'_services_2_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(161,35,'services_2_heading','Security Hardening'),(162,35,'_services_2_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(163,35,'services_2_body','Keep your users, site, and data safe from harm. I make it extra difficult to hack so they move on to an easier target.'),(164,35,'_services_2_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(165,35,'services_3_icon','fa-wrench fa-3x'),(166,35,'_services_3_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(167,35,'services_3_heading','Maintenance'),(168,35,'_services_3_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(169,35,'services_3_body','Your website is a well oiled machine with many moving parts. Don’t allow advancements in technology to grind its gears. I can keep it compatible and optimized for tools of the next generation.'),(170,35,'_services_3_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(171,35,'services_4_icon','fa-pencil-square-o fa-3x'),(172,35,'_services_4_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(173,35,'services_4_heading','Alterations'),(174,35,'_services_4_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(175,35,'services_4_body','Already have a website but want to change things, or add new features? I can keep your site aligned with your evolving requirements. '),(176,35,'_services_4_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(177,35,'services_5_icon','fa-magic fa-3x'),(178,35,'_services_5_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(179,35,'services_5_heading','Custom Anything'),(180,35,'_services_5_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(181,35,'services_5_body','Have an idea for a novel feature or a new App? I can write the code to make it happen. Is your idea BIG? no problem, I have a large network of industry professionals to build a team. Your options are nearly limitless.'),(182,35,'_services_5_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(183,35,'services','6'),(184,35,'_services','field_5a473aeb6726a'),(185,65,'hero_image','64'),(186,65,'_h