ts and be approved before it goes into the live site. This structured release process reduces risks, enables simple rollbacks, and allows phased release rollouts. Catch bugs before your users see them and prevent downtime due to human error.'),(964,87,'_features_4_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(965,87,'features_5_icon','fa-line-chart fa-fw'),(966,87,'_features_5_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(967,87,'features_5_heading','Analytics'),(968,87,'_features_5_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(969,87,'features_5_body','Information that helps you learn how people use your website, and where they are from. Make evidence based decisions that improve your website to provide users with more value and a better experience. Your website will integrate with Google Analytics so that you always have the best information.'),(970,87,'_features_5_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(971,87,'features','6'),(972,87,'_features','field_5a474441c90a9'),(973,87,'quote_bar_body','\"The original idea of the web was that it should be a collaborative space where you can communicate through sharing information.\"'),(974,87,'_quote_bar_body','field_5a47459b6956d'),(975,87,'quote_bar_cite','- Tim Berners-Lee'),(976,87,'_quote_bar_cite','field_5a4745d46956e'),(977,87,'quote_bar',''),(978,87,'_quote_bar','field_5a4745776956c'),(979,87,'cost_heading','\"OK, so how much does it cost?\"'),(980,87,'_cost_heading','field_5a4764d9370f2'),(981,87,'cost_body','It depends and varies based on requirements. I provide free consultancy to learn what you want to accomplish and provide sensible options to make it happen. Then you get a quote based on the information I learn from this discovery phase. I wish it was easier, but making up numbers serves nobody and would be misleading.'),(982,87,'_cost_body','field_5a4764e7370f3'),(983,87,'cost_cta','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:39:\"Give me a shout and let’s get started\";s:3:\"url\";s:30:\"http://derulski.local/contact/\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(984,87,'_cost_cta','field_5a4764fb3