b0a6726c'),(1153,123,'services_3_body','Your website is a well oiled machine with many moving parts. Don’t allow advancements in technology to grind its gears. I can keep it compatible and optimized for tools of the next generation.'),(1154,123,'_services_3_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1155,123,'services_4_icon','fa-pencil-square-o fa-3x'),(1156,123,'_services_4_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1157,123,'services_4_heading','Alterations'),(1158,123,'_services_4_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1159,123,'services_4_body','Already have a website but want to change things, or add new features? I can keep your site aligned with your evolving requirements. '),(1160,123,'_services_4_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1161,123,'services_5_icon','fa-magic fa-3x'),(1162,123,'_services_5_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1163,123,'services_5_heading','Custom Anything'),(1164,123,'_services_5_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1165,123,'services_5_body','Have an idea for a novel feature or a new App? I can write the code to make it happen. Is your idea BIG? no problem, I have a large network of industry professionals to build a team. Your options are nearly limitless.'),(1166,123,'_services_5_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1167,123,'services','6'),(1168,123,'_services','field_5a473aeb6726a'),(1169,123,'features_0_icon','fa-wordpress fa-fw'),(1170,123,'_features_0_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1171,123,'features_0_heading','Content Management'),(1172,123,'_features_0_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1173,123,'features_0_body','Manage all your content with the simplicity and intuitiveness of WordPress. It’s so simple that you will wonder why all software isn’t this way. But, it does not have to be WordPress if another technology is more sensible to meet your requirements.'),(1174,123,'_features_0_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1175,123,'features_1_icon','fa-mobile fa-fw'),(1176,123,'_features_1_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1177,123,'features_1_heading','Device Agnostic'),(1178,123,'_features_