uctured release process reduces risks, enables simple rollbacks, and allows phased release rollouts. Catch bugs before your users see them and prevent downtime due to human error.'),(1198,123,'_features_4_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1199,123,'features_5_icon','fa-line-chart fa-fw'),(1200,123,'_features_5_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1201,123,'features_5_heading','Analytics'),(1202,123,'_features_5_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1203,123,'features_5_body','Information that helps you learn how people use your website, and where they are from. Make evidence based decisions that improve your website to provide users with more value and a better experience. Your website will integrate with Google Analytics so that you always have the best information.'),(1204,123,'_features_5_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1205,123,'features','6'),(1206,123,'_features','field_5a474441c90a9'),(1207,123,'quote_bar_body','\"The original idea of the web was that it should be a collaborative space where you can communicate through sharing information.\"'),(1208,123,'_quote_bar_body','field_5a47459b6956d'),(1209,123,'quote_bar_cite','- Tim Berners-Lee'),(1210,123,'_quote_bar_cite','field_5a4745d46956e'),(1211,123,'quote_bar',''),(1212,123,'_quote_bar','field_5a4745776956c'),(1213,123,'cost_heading','\"OK, so how much does it cost?\"'),(1214,123,'_cost_heading','field_5a4764d9370f2'),(1215,123,'cost_body','It depends and varies based on requirements. I provide free consultancy to learn what you want to accomplish and provide sensible options to make it happen. Then you get a quote based on the information I learn from this discovery phase. I wish it was easier, but making up numbers serves nobody and would be misleading.'),(1216,123,'_cost_body','field_5a4764e7370f3'),(1217,123,'cost_cta','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:39:\"Give me a shout and let’s get started\";s:3:\"url\";s:30:\"http://derulski.local/contact/\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(1218,123,'_cost_cta','field_5a4764fb370f4'),(1219,123,'cost',''),(1220,123,'_cost','field_5a4764c5370f1'),(1221,123,'recent_posts_heading','Recent Posts'),(1222,123,'_recent_posts_heading','field_5a47754c67e42'),(1223,123,'hero_sub_text','From Maciej Derulski & Associates'),(1224,123,'_hero_sub_text','field_5a48504513768'),(1225,124,'hero_image','64'),(1226,124,'_hero_image','field_5a473a942f2c2'),(1227,124,'hero_heading','Elegant solutions for your Web presence.'),(1228,124,'_hero_heading','field_5a473ab92f2c3'),(1229,124,'hero',''),(1230,124,'_hero','field_5a473a763156b'),(1231,124,'services_0_icon','fa-code fa-3x'),(1232,124,'_services_0_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1233,124,'services_0_heading','Website Development'),(1234,124,'_services_0_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1235,124,'services_0_body','Need a new website but not sure where to start? I can help turn your ideas into a site tailored to your unique requirements.'),(1236,124,'_services_0_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1237,124,'services_1_icon','fa-tachometer fa-3x'),(1238,124,'_services_1_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1239,124,'services_1_heading','Speed Optimization'),(1240,124,'_services_1_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1241,124,'services_1_body','Stop wasting peoples time and data plans. Loading time now impacts your Google PageRank. I can make most pages load in under 1 second.'),(1242,124,'_services_1_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1243,124,'services_2_icon','fa-lock fa-3x'),(1244,124,'_services_2_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1245,124,'services_2_heading','Security Hardening'),(1246,124,'_services_2_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1247,124,'services_2_body','Keep your users, site, and data safe from harm. I make it extra difficult to hack so they move on to an easier target.'),(1248,124,'_services_2_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1249,124,'services_3_icon','fa-wrench fa-3x'),(1250,124,'_services_3_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1251,124,'services_3_heading','Maintenance'),(1252,124,'_services_3_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1253,124,'services_3_body','Your website is a well oiled machine with many moving parts. Don’t allow advancements in technology to grind its gears. I can keep it compatible and optimized for tools of the next generation.'),(1254,124,'_services_3_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1255,124,'services_4_icon','fa-pencil-square-o fa-3x'),(1256,124,'_services_4_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1257,124,'services_4_heading','Alterations'),(1258,124,'_services_4_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1259,124,'services_4_body','Already have a website but want to change things, or add new features? I can keep your site aligned with your evolving requirements. '),(1260,124,'_services_4_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1261,124,'services_5_icon','fa-magic fa-3x'),(1262,124,'_services_5_icon','field_5a473afe6726b'),(1263,124,'services_5_heading','Custom Anything'),(1264,124,'_services_5_heading','field_5a473b0a6726c'),(1265,124,'services_5_body','Have an idea for a novel feature or a new App? I can write the code to make it happen. Is your idea BIG? no problem, I have a large network of industry professionals to build a team. Your options are nearly limitless.'),(1266,124,'_services_5_body','field_5a473b1b6726d'),(1267,124,'services','6'),(1268,124,'_services','field_5a473aeb6726a'),(1269,124,'features_0_icon','fa-wordpress fa-fw'),(1270,124,'_features_0_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1271,124,'features_0_heading','Content Management'),(1272,124,'_features_0_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1273,124,'features_0_body','Manage all your content with the simplicity and intuitiveness of WordPress. It’s so simple that you will wonder why all software isn’t this way. But, it does not have to be WordPress if another technology is more sensible to meet your requirements.'),(1274,124,'_features_0_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1275,124,'features_1_icon','fa-mobile fa-fw'),(1276,124,'_features_1_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1277,124,'features_1_heading','Device Agnostic'),(1278,124,'_features_1_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1279,124,'features_1_body','Fully responsive design that adapts to the users screen size. Your website will make the best use of available screen real estate and deliver your users an experience optimized for their device.'),(1280,124,'_features_1_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1281,124,'features_2_icon','fa-universal-access fa-fw'),(1282,124,'_features_2_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1283,124,'features_2_heading','Accessibility'),(1284,124,'_features_2_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1285,124,'features_2_body','Everyone should be able to use, perceive, and interact with your website regardless of their abilities or disabilities. Deliver optimized content for assistive technologies and provide a great experience for users of all life circumstances. Your website will meet or exceed <i>WCAG 2.0 Level AA</i> as required by the <i>Accessibility for Ontarians with Disabilities Act, 2005</i>.'),(1286,124,'_features_2_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1287,124,'features_3_icon','fa-github fa-fw'),(1288,124,'_features_3_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1289,124,'features_3_heading','Source Code Management'),(1290,124,'_features_3_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1291,124,'features_3_body','Your website’s code will be version controlled so that each edit and its details are logged. Code can be reverted to any previous state, and multiple developers can coordinate and merge their work with ease. Your source code is the magic that makes your website a reality. Version control helps prevent disasters and allows quick recovery.'),(1292,124,'_features_3_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1293,124,'features_4_icon','fa-cubes fa-fw'),(1294,124,'_features_4_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1295,124,'features_4_heading','Multi-Tier Deployments'),(1296,124,'_features_4_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1297,124,'features_4_body','New or revised code is deployed to a testing site where it must pass all tests and be approved before it goes into the live site. This structured release process reduces risks, enables simple rollbacks, and allows phased release rollouts. Catch bugs before your users see them and prevent downtime due to human error.'),(1298,124,'_features_4_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1299,124,'features_5_icon','fa-line-chart fa-fw'),(1300,124,'_features_5_icon','field_5a474441c90aa'),(1301,124,'features_5_heading','Analytics'),(1302,124,'_features_5_heading','field_5a474441c90ab'),(1303,124,'features_5_body','Information that helps you learn how people use your website, and where they are from. Make evidence based decisions that improve your website to provide users with more value and a better experience. Your website will integrate with Google Analytics so that you always have the best information.'),(1304,124,'_features_5_body','field_5a474441c90ac'),(1305,124,'features','6'),(1306,124,'_features','field_5a474441c90a9'),(1307,124,'quote_bar_body','\"The original idea of the web was that it should be a collaborative space where you can communicate through sharing information.\"'),(1308,124,'_quote_bar_body','field_5a47459b6956d'),(1309,124,'quote_bar_cite','- Tim Berners-Lee'),(1310,124,'_quote_bar_cite','field_5a4745d46956e'),(1311,124,'quote_bar',''),(1312,124,'_quote_bar','field_5a4745776956c'),(1313,124,'cost_heading','\"OK, so how much does it cost?\"'),(1314,124,'_cost_heading','field_5a4764d9370f2'),(1315,124,'cost_body','It depends and varies based on requirements. I provide free consultancy to learn what you want to accomplish and provide sensible options to make it happen. Then you get a quote based on the information I learn from this discovery phase. I wish it was easier, but making up numbers serves nobody and would be misleading.'),(1316,124,'_cost_body','field_5a4764e7370f3'),(1317,124,'cost_cta','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:39:\"Give me a shout and let’s get started\";s:3:\"url\";s:30:\"http://derulski.local/contact/\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(1318,124,'_cost_cta','field_5a4764fb370f4'),(1319,124,'cost',''),(1320,124,'_cost','field_5a47